                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 702.6211/288.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Governor
                            <persName type="to">Lister</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-05-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 14, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I thank you for your telegram of May 13. I may inform you that German Ambassador
                    has taken steps to transfer the German Consul at Seattle to another post.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">W. J. Bryan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
